      • getCriteriaDescription

        protected java.lang.String getCriteriaDescription()
        Description copied from class: SequentialGetStepSupplier
        Returns string description of the defined criteria. If there is some description and Predicate#toString() returns some human-readable value then method returns this value. When criteria is defined then it returns '<not described condition>'. When criteria is not defined then an empty string is returned.
